<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome to Pro · Resilience Weather</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@700&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:#001433;color:#F0F6FF;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:24px;}
.card{max-width:440px;width:100%;background:rgba(74,158,255,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(74,158,255,0.3);border-radius:24px;padding:48px 32px;}
.icon{font-size:56px;margin-bottom:20px;animation:pop 0.5s ease;}
@keyframes pop{0%{transform:scale(0.5);opacity:0}80%{transform:scale(1.1)}100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}
h1{font-size:28px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:10px;}
p{font-size:14px;color:#94A3B8;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.6;}
a{display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;background:#4A9EFF;color:#001433;border-radius:12px;font-weight:900;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;}
a:hover{background:#6FB3FF;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="icon">⚡</div>
  <h1>You're Pro now.</h1>
  <p>Your subscription is active. Welcome to the full Resilience Weather suite — zero ads, live radar, advanced intelligence, and everything else.</p>
  <a href="/">Open Dashboard →</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
